org.fcrepo.auth

Class ServletContainerAuthenticationProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fcrepo.auth.ServletContainerAuthenticationProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.modeshape.jcr.security.AuthenticationProvider

    public class ServletContainerAuthenticationProvider
extends Object
implements org.modeshape.jcr.security.AuthenticationProvider
    Authenticates ModeShape logins where servlet credentials are supplied. Capable of authenticating whether or not container has performed user authentication. This is a singleton with an injected policy enforcement point. The singleton pattern allows ModeShape to obtain this instance via classname configuration.
    Author:
    Gregory Jansen
